comes flying at you?

44:00.634 --> 44:02.566
What if another puck...

44:02.568 --> 44:05.204
Oh, you're just gonna
hit it away like that?

44:07.472 --> 44:08.905
Oh.

44:08.907 --> 44:11.612
Oh-ho-ho-ho. Rhett!

44:12.911 --> 44:14.479
