Oh, no, no, no, no!

46:31.851 --> 46:34.584
Stop him!
No, no, no, no, no!

46:34.586 --> 46:37.021
Get back! Wesley!

46:37.023 --> 46:41.361
That is what I'm trying to say. I think clearly
the dog has some sort of anxiety disorder.

46:43.362 --> 46:44.561
Wes.

46:44.563 --> 46:46.563
Kenneth,
I have to call you back.

46:46.565 --> 46:51.668
