47:33.813 --> 47:37.715
They were not strangers.
It was doggy day care.

47:37.717 --> 47:40.050
You could have called me.
I would have taken him.

47:40.052 --> 47:42.519
But it was not
your day to have him.

47:42.521 --> 47:46.523
