49:45.778 --> 49:48.380
Hung on for dear life.

49:53.719 --> 49:55.487
It's, um...

49:57.822 --> 50:00.891
This is nice, right?

50:02.762 --> 50:03.760
I know, I know.

50:03.762 --> 50:06.130
- He's getting impatient.
- Okay.

50:06.132 --> 50:07.664
Up top.

50:07.666 --> 50:10.300
Ooh, man.
How about you? Ah!

